OL,6,FA disqualified driver who killed a
OL,7,Ftoddler and left his mother in a coma
OL,8,Fin hospital after ploughing into their
OL,9,Fcar has been jailed.
OL,11,FSharjeel Shahzad, aged 30, was behind
OL,12,Fthe wheel of a stolen Porsche Cayenne
OL,13,Fwhen he crashed head-on into a Toyota
OL,14,FAuris containing two-year-old Shehbaz
OL,15,FSingh, his parents Kushpreet Kaur and
OL,16,FAmritpal Singh, and their close
OL,17,Ffriends Baljit Singh and Pavanpreet
OL,18,FKaur.
