OL,3,CDriver crashed into family and killed
OL,4,Ctoddler after stealing Porsche
OL,6,FThe toddler died at Birmingham
OL,7,FChildren's Hospital following the
OL,8,Fcollision on Dartmouth Road,
OL,9,FSmethwick, which took place just
OL,10,Fbefore 11pm on December 14 last year -
OL,11,Fwhile his mother remains unconscious
OL,12,Fin hospital to this day having
OL,13,Fsuffered life-changing injuries.
OL,15,FShahzad, from Great Barr, ran away
OL,16,Ffrom the collision but was arrested
OL,17,Ftwo days later after forensic
OL,18,Fexaminations discovered his finger
OL,19,Fprints on the false number plate of
OL,20,Fthe Porsche and his DNA from the
OL,21,Fvehicle's airbag.
