OL,3,CDriver crashed into family and killed
OL,4,Ctoddler after stealing Porsche
OL,6,FHe initially denied causing death by
OL,7,Fdangerous driving but changed his plea
OL,8,Fto guilty in April.
OL,10,FShahzad also admitted two charges of
OL,11,Fcausing serious injury by dangerous
OL,12,Fdriving, driving whilst disqualified,
OL,13,Fdriving with no insurance and failing
OL,14,Fto stop after a collision.
OL,16,FHe had clocked speeds of 51mph in a
OL,17,F30mph zone and drove on the wrong side
OL,18,Fof the road leading up to the fatal
OL,19,Fsmash.
