OL,3,CDriver crashed into family and killed
OL,4,Ctoddler after stealing Porsche
OL,6,FA total of eight finger prints were
OL,7,Fdiscovered on the false number plate,
OL,8,Fwhile the Porsche had been taken from
OL,9,Fnearby Walsall during a sales test.
OL,11,FShehbaz and his family had been
OL,12,Ftravelling home from attending a
OL,13,Ffamily's birthday when the collision
OL,14,Fhappened.
OL,16,FShehbaz was in the back of the Toyota
OL,17,Fwith his parents and was being held in
OL,18,Fhis dad's arms, Wolverhampton Crown
OL,19,FCourt heard.
