OL,3,CDriver crashed into family and killed
OL,4,Ctoddler after stealing Porsche
OL,6,FThe Toyota was driven by Baljit Singh,
OL,7,Fwho was also seriously injured.
OL,9,FShahzad had a history of driving
OL,10,Foffences and appeared before
OL,11,FMagistrates' in May last year for
OL,12,Fdriving without a licence or insurance.
OL,14,FHis offending got worse when, on June
OL,15,F10 last year, he took police on a high-
OL,16,Fspeed chase on the M42 after making
OL,17,Foff in a Audi A4 Avant that had been
OL,18,Fbeen advertised on Facebook in Belton,
OL,19,FLeicestershire.
