OL,3,CDriver crashed into family and killed
OL,4,Ctoddler after stealing Porsche
OL,6,FAfter reaching speeds of nearly 150mph
OL,7,Fand swerving through motorway cones,
OL,8,Fhe was only stopped when police were
OL,9,Fforced to crash into him, injuring an
OL,10,Fofficer in the process.
OL,12,FShahzad appeared at Wolverhampton
OL,13,FCrown Court on Friday where he was
OL,14,Fsentenced for the fatal Smethwick
OL,15,Fcrash and the June 10 police chase.
OL,17,FJudge Jonathan Gosling ordered him to
OL,18,Fserve 15 years and four months behind
OL,19,Fbars, after giving him 20 per cent
OL,20,Fcredit for his later guilty pleas.
