OL,3,CDriver crashed into family and killed
OL,4,Ctoddler after stealing Porsche
OL,6,FThe judge told him: "You have
OL,7,Fdestroyed the lives on Amritpal and
OL,8,FKushpreet and devastated their family
OL,9,Fand friends.
OL,11,F"You killed that little boy and
OL,12,Fseriously injured other people in the
OL,13,Fcar.
OL,15,F"Your true character was revealed by
OL,16,Fwhat you did afterwards, just as you
OL,17,Fdid on June 10."
OL,19,FShahzad was also banned from driving
OL,20,Ffor 18 years and three months.
